        Amendment, by leave, withdrawn.
      </p>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_8gc' title='Col. 8GC &mdash; HL Deb 28 February 1996 vol 569 c8GC' name='column_8gc' href='#column_8gc' rel='bookmark'>8GC</a>
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0569P0-06176'>
