      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0569P0-06217'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0569P0_19960228_GCR_105' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Amendment, by leave, withdrawn.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0569P0-06218'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0569P0_19960228_GCR_106' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Lord Fraser of Carmyllie</span> moved Amendment No.10:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0569P0-06219'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0569P0_19960228_GCR_107' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Page 14, line 18, leave out from ("arbitration") to end of line 20 and insert&#x2014;
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0569P0-06220'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0569P0_19960228_GCR_108' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        ("This power shall not be exercised on the ground that the party Is&#x2014;
        <ol>
        <li>(a) an individual ordinarily resident outside the United Kingdom, or</li>
        <li>(b) a corporation or association incorporated or formed under the law of a country outside the United Kingdom, or whose central management and control is exercised outside the United Kingdom.").</li></ol>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0569P0-06221'>
