        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0569P0_19960228_GCR_113' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 45 [<span class="italic">Determination of preliminary point of law</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0569P0-06226'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0569P0_19960228_GCR_114' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
